data.description: Welcome to modern living in Lynchburg's Stonehaven community! Tucked off Old Forest Road convenient to all Lynchburg has to offer, this beautiful two-story home features an elegant style inside and out. With over 1540 SF of livable space, this plan has been one of the most popular in the neighborhood thus far. Spacious living room and kitchen area with separate dining space on the first floor perfect for entertaining guests. Rear covered patio perfect for relaxing. Upstairs features 3 bedrooms and laundry area. Primary bedroom offers a large walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom. Don't miss your chance to see this beautiful home!
